   - `claude_code_args(prompt, model)` - builds `-p {prompt} --output-format stream-json [--model ...]`
   - `cursor_args(prompt, model)` - builds `--prompt {prompt} [--model ...]`
   - `set_agent_env(cmd, agent_cli, agent_token)` - sets ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or CURSOR_API_KEY, CI=1
